    Bus
    Bus class used for temporarly storing values between registers.
    Byte
    Low-leve class for storing a single byte of information, 8-bits.
    Controller
    The hardware controler for driving input path.
    CPU

    Flags
    Flags class keeps all of the 4 flags and updates them based on current Instruction
    Helper
    Helper class provides all the arithmetic and logical operations that are used by ALU
